      <h2>Best Lifetime Free Credit Cards in India</h2>
      <p>Lifetime free credit cards (LTF cards) are the smartest choice for budget-conscious consumers who want card benefits without paying annual fees. These cards charge absolutely nothing — no joining fee, no annual fee, no hidden charges — for the entire lifetime of the card. And contrary to popular belief, many LTF cards offer excellent rewards, cashback, and perks that rival mid-tier paid cards.</p>
      <p>In 2026, India's best lifetime free cards include the ICICI Amazon Pay card (5% for Prime members), Axis ACE (5% on utility bills), IDFC First WOW (zero forex markup), and AU Small Finance Lit Card (lifetime free with lounge access). These cards prove that free doesn't mean basic — you can get genuine value without spending a rupee on card fees.</p>

      <h2>Key Features of Lifetime Free Cards</h2>
      <ul class="feature-list">
        <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> <strong>Zero Annual Fee:</strong> No joining fee and no annual renewal charges for the entire life of the card</li>
        <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> <strong>No Spending Conditions:</strong> Unlike fee-waiver cards, LTF cards don't require minimum annual spends to keep them free</li>
        <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> <strong>Genuine Rewards:</strong> Earn 1-5% cashback or equivalent reward points on all transactions</li>
        <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> <strong>Fuel Surcharge Waiver:</strong> Most LTF cards include 1% fuel surcharge waiver on petrol pump transactions</li>
        <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> <strong>EMI Conversion:</strong> Convert large purchases to easy EMIs at low interest rates, same as paid cards</li>
        <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> <strong>Build Credit Score:</strong> Perfect first credit card to build a strong credit history at zero cost</li>
      </ul>

